---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Welcome from "../components/Welcome.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";   
import { CldImage } from 'astro-cloudinary';
---

<Layout>
  <Welcome />  <!-- Footer-like contact section at bottom -->

  <div class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-8 px-4 md:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Thinkin' Rocks is where deep-tech ideas become working prototypes.
        </p>
      
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Brilliant engineers are not limited by imagination - they're limited by access.  
          Access to hardware, compute, labs, and experts. We are fixing that. Think of us as a <a href="/space" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 transition-colors">hardware library + build ecosystem</a>.  
          A place filled with cutting-edge tools - from neurowearables and humanoid
          robots to edge AI compute and FPGAs - where anyone can experiment, test ideas,
          and build real prototypes with real hardware.
          By opening access to advanced tooling and engineering mentors, we accelerate the
          deep-tech pipeline. 
          Our goal is clear: become Finland’s hub for applied innovation.</b>
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Since our launch in 2025, we've built partnerships with world-class tech
          companies — including Varjo, Tenstorrent, Doublepoint, and Alif Semiconductor.
          We host hands-on build sessions where engineers learn new tools, share knowledge,
          and turn ideas into functioning prototypes.
        </p>
      
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Next: more hardware, more build cycles, more prototypes shipped.
        </p>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Built by engineers, for engineers.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-2 mb-10">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32  mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden ">
              <CldImage
                src="milana-min_yrnyld"
                alt="Milana"
                class="w-32 h-32 object-cover"
                width={256}
                height={256}
                priority
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Milana</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto"><span class="font-mono text-indigo-500">tg: <a href="https://t.me/katteelsker" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">@katteelsker</a></span><br>can't live without coffee and anime. watched one piece twice.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200  mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden ">
              <CldImage
                src="yerzhan-min_gl7gur"
                alt="Yerzhan"
                class="w-32 h-32 object-cover"
                width={256}
                height={256}
                priority
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Yerzhan</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto"> <span class="font-mono text-indigo-500">tg: <a href="https://t.me/yerzham" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">@yerzham</a></span><br>applied for Y-combinator before it became mainstream.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden ">
              <CldImage
                src="alex-min_ypkkz2"
                alt="Alex"
                class="w-32 h-32 object-cover"
                width={256}
                height={256}
                priority
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Alex</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto"><span class="font-mono text-indigo-500">tg: <a href="https://t.me/alexocc" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">@alexocc</a></span><br>started learning english to understand computer errors.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200  mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden ">
              <CldImage
                src="daniyar-min_kok519"
                alt="Daniyar"
                class="w-32 h-32 object-cover"
                width={256}
                height={256}
                priority
              />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Daniyar</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto"><span class="font-mono text-indigo-500">tg: <a href="https://t.me/UhOhOhNo" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">@UhOhOhNo</a></span><br>coding since 7th grade, still pretending to know what hardware is.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-mono text-gray-400">A</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Arthur</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto"><span class="font-mono text-indigo-500">tg: <a href="https://t.me/ktnlvr" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">@ktnlvr</a></span><br>knows just enough math to be dangerous.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl font-mono text-gray-400">V</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Vlad</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto"><span class="font-mono text-indigo-500">tg: <a href="https://t.me/VladyslavBM" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">@VladyslavBM</a></span><br>bio coming soon.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <a href="mailto:milana.begantsova@aaltoes.com" class="block">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 mx-auto mb-2 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gray-300 transition-colors">
                <span class="text-2xl font-mono text-gray-500">+</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Join Us</h3>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Partners Section -->
      <div class="mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          We work with industry leaders to bring cutting-edge technology directly to students:
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4  text-center">
            <a href="https://varjo.com/" target="_blank">
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <img 
                src="/images/companies-logo/varjo.png" 
                alt="Varjo" 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
              />
            </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 text-center">
            <a href="https://doublepoint.com/" target="_blank"> 
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
                <img 
                  src="/images/companies-logo/doublepoint.png" 
                  alt="Doublepoint" 
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              
            </div>
          </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 text-center">
            <a href="https://alifsemi.com/" target="_blank">
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <img 
                src="/images/companies-logo/Alif_Semiconductor_logo.webp" 
                alt="Alif Semiconductor" 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain"
              />
            </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <a 
            href="mailto:milana@thinkinrocks.com?subject=Partnership%20Opportunity&body=Hi%20Milana,%0D%0A%0D%0AI'm%20interested%20in%20exploring%20a%20partnership%20opportunity%20with%20Thinkin'%20Rocks.%0D%0A%0D%0ACompany:%20[Your%20Company]%0D%0ATechnology/Hardware:%20[What%20you%20can%20provide]%0D%0AContact:%20[Your%20contact%20information]%0D%0A%0D%0ABest%20regards,"
            class="block bg-gray-100 p-3 md:p-4 text-center hover:bg-gray-200 hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors"
          >
            <div class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-mono text-gray-400">+</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <div class="text-center fade-in">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-indigo-600 h-fit translate-0.5">
            <a 
              href="https://discord.gg/5MEu6njksN" 
              class="bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 inline-flex px-6 py-3 -translate-0.5 items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-mono hover:bg-indigo-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Join Us
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-600 h-fit translate-0.5">
            <a 
              href="mailto:milana@thinkinrocks.com" 
              class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 inline-flex px-6 py-3 -translate-0.5 items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-mono hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
